This study demonstrated the method of correction for GBS genotype to improve the accuracy of GBS data, following the previous studies [9–14]. This correction method resulted in GBSc genotype type and GBSc genotype dosage. The GBSc genotype type was derived from rounding the GBSc genotype dosage. The inferred GBSc genotype dosage of genotype aa was \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
